GridX is an incubation project under Dojo Toolkit(http://www.dojotoolkit.org/), it's also being worked closely with dgrid(https://github.com/kriszyp/dgrid) for the new Dojo Grid.

GridX is still in development phase, features are experimental and subject to API changes.

Please put and run gridx in parallel with dojo/dijit/dojox folder.